<p style="font-size: 12.5px">
    <strong>Prop A:</strong> $535M Earthquake Safety &amp;
    Emergency Response Bond (2/3 needed).
    <strong>Prop B:</strong> Lifetime term limits for Mayor
    &amp; Supervisors. <strong>Prop C:</strong> Reduces business
    tax / softens top-executive-pay tax (industry-backed).
    <strong>Prop D:</strong> Increases business tax on companies
    with high CEO-to-median-worker pay ratios (labor-backed). C
    and D are competing — higher vote-getter prevails.
</p>
<div class="scroll">
    <table>
        <colgroup>
            <col style="width: 26%" />
            {%- for p in race.props %}
            <col style="width: 18%" />
            {%- endfor %}
        </colgroup>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Organization</th>
                {%- for p in race.props %}
                <th>{{ p.label }}</th>
                {%- endfor %}
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {%- for e in race.endorsements %}
            <tr>
                <td><a href="{{ e.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ e.org }}</a></td>
                {%- for p in race.props %}
                {%- set v = e.votes[p.id] %}
                {%- if v == "none" %}
                <td class="none">X</td>
                {%- elif v == "yes" %}
                <td class="yes">YES</td>
                {%- elif v == "no" %}
                <td class="no">NO</td>
                {%- endif %}
                {%- endfor %}
            </tr>
            {%- endfor %}
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
